high_descs: Move to the table to the left of you
Pick up a tomato from the table
Move to the fridge behind you
Chill the tomato for a moment in the fridge
Move to the table to the left of the fridge
Put the tomato on the table
anns.task_desc: Put a chilled tomato on the table to the left of the fridge.

high_descs: Turn around and walk toward the table to the right.
Pick up the tomato off of the table.
Turn around and walk to the refrigerator.
Cool the tomato in the refrigerator for a few seconds and take it back out.
Turn left and walk to the dining table with a loaf of bread on it.
Put the tomato on the dining table, in front of the loaf of bread.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooled tomato on a dining table.

high_descs: Turn to your right then cross the room head to the table beside the stove
Pick up the tomato on the table beside toaster
Turn to your left then walk towards the fridge
Open the fridge put in and out the tomato then close the fridge
Turn to your left then walk straight  towards the table on your right
Put the tomato on the edge of the table
anns.task_desc: Put the chilled tomato on the table
